snippet.title: Nidhogg 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
AVAILABLE NOW!

PS4 -- https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/nidhogg-2/cid=UP2143-CUSA07640_00-NIDHOGG2GAMEPLAY

STEAM --  http://store.steampowered.com/app/535520/Nidhogg_2/

The wurm has returned and it must feed! Shed your garments and paint the walls with the flesh of your enemies, for only one can be worthy of sacrifice. 

"Hog Knuckles" by Mux Mool - Courtesy of Ghostly
